<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Bookcrossing</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload", defer: true %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
 
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="container-md mt-3">
      <%= render 'shared/menu' %>
    </div>   
 
    <main class="container-md mt-3">

      <div class="p-4 p-md-5 mb-4 text-bg-dark">
        <div class="col-md-6 px-0">
          <h1 class="display-4 fst-italic">Буккроссинг - это весело</h1>
          <p class="lead my-3">Здесь можно вставить рандомные цитаты из словаря. А бэкграунд картинка</p>
        </div>
      </div>      
  
      <%= yield %>

    </main>

    <footer class="py-3 my-4">
        <ul class="nav justify-content-center border-bottom pb-3 mb-3">
            <li><%= link_to 'Главная', root_path, class: "nav-link px-2 text-black" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to 'Про нас', about_path, class: "nav-link px-2 text-black"%></li>
            <li><%= link_to 'Контакты', contact_path, class: "nav-link px-2 text-black"%></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-center text-muted">&copy; @nikolai_mikhaylov <%= Time.now.year %></p>
    </footer>    

  </body>
</html>
